data.description: Nestled in the serene Arlington Heights neighborhood, this meticulously maintained mid-century modern home offers 2,761 square feet of classic design blended seamlessly with contemporary updates. With four bedrooms, two and a half baths, and a prime location near Wildwood Park, this property provides the perfect mix of style, space, and convenience. Inside, the open floor plan, hardwood floors, and a remodeled kitchen with custom cabinets create a welcoming atmosphere. The main-floor primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom and custom closets, while the fourth bedroom downstairs offers its own separate exterior access, adding versatility to the layout. The front deck provides a perfect space for outdoor relaxation. A new roof installed in Spring 2023 enhances value and peace of mind. Located just minutes from downtown, this home presents a unique opportunity to enjoy mid-century living with modern comforts. [Home Energy Score = 2. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10221776]
